ing high-resolution transmission\nspectroscopy to further our understanding of how atmospheric characteristics\nvary over a diverse sample of exoplanets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 May 2022 17:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Jul 2022 17:59:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-05"}
