ves. The theoretical results in this study\nare supported by experimental data collected in a towing tank at the Australian\nMaritime College using model versions of the standard Wigley hulls and Wigley\ntransom-stern hulls.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 May 2022 03:20:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Mar 2023 02:29:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-28"}
